    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You manifest a pair of icy crystal wings before you to use as a bow, and fire an arrow of ice to pierce through your target.</em></p><p>Make a ranged Ninjutsu attack against a creature within range, dealing 12d6 Cold damage. A creature hit by this must make a Constitution saving throw, becoming <em><strong>Stunned</strong></em> until the start of their turn next round and gaining a rank of <em><strong>Chilled</strong></em> upon failure, or no additional effect on success. When a creature Stunned by this Jutsu is damaged in any way, they are no longer <em><strong>Stunned</strong></em>, and take 2d6 Cold damage per rank of <em><strong>Chilled</strong></em> they have and lose all ranks of <em><strong>Chilled</strong></em>.</p><p></p>",
